{"type": "article", "id": 31323, "title": "像收信一样收一份巧克力｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2016-08-22T23:27:39Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 31807, "name": "IDIO"}, {"id": 31808, "name": "Fairy Fastener"}, {"id": 31809, "name": "Tiny Atlas Quarterly"}, {"id": 31810, "name": "Alite Design"}, {"id": 31811, "name": "Da-sein"}, {"id": 31812, "name": "Permafrost"}, {"id": 31813, "name": "Love Cocoa"}, {"id": 31814, "name": "Suzuki Kabuki"}, {"id": 31815, "name": "Petter Knudsen"}, {"id": 31816, "name": "James Cadbury"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 136, "image": "img/article/article_show/201608230029023QkyWudIHTx0PKw8.jpeg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Looper by IDIO Creative Works, Inc.</h3><p>如果你在入手追踪器时因为它们并不美观的外型而犹豫不决，IDIO 工作室研发的这款 Looper 或许会改变你对这类产品的看法，将时尚与科技结合起来。和其他追踪器不同，小小的设备元件外包覆着流苏形状的皮革，讨喜的外观让它看上去更像是一个时尚的配件。Looper 通过内嵌的蓝牙传感器与智能手机连接在一起，只要在它的范围内就能通过配套的应用随时查找到设备的具体位置，还可以控制追踪器发出尖锐的提示音，方便查找。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1278752687/looper-fashion-meets-smart-tracker-technology\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与众筹，早鸟价为 39 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160823003342vmOHrwcBNAdCn2a0.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.521355\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160823003339GITnEVQdKbaSCOc0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563235\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160823003340nvB9bgwIUf1mO8u5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562592\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160823003341EQGwIgj5Yr9cqBxJ.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.316642\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><p><br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160823003339xU0B7VuMjQGlZRO8.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.564706\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Bracelet Fairy by Fairy Fastener</h3><p>一个人的时候想要顺利地戴上手链可不是一件容易的事情，为了让人们能够单手解决这一难题，由来自加拿大的三胞胎姐妹成立的 <a href=\"https://fairyfastener.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Fairy Fastener</a> 就推出了一款名为 Bracelet Fairy 的辅助工具。只需要用它的橡胶制的尖嘴钳夹住手链一端，放在手心，另一只手就能轻松地把手链扣好。Bracelet Fairy 的棒身采用了符合人体工程学的设计，弧度契合手掌的形状，提供了舒适的握感。这是它的<a href=\"https://fairyfastener.com/product/bracelet-fairy/\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 19.95 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160823003316J3alm7sTqPd8IWwL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.706522\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160823003316CWNpm2linGhIYVAX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666439\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160823003316yW3zmQAlqrcp7iD4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666439\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160823003316rv3pAiJaIcCw42je.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.746939\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>SOLAS Camera Bag by Tiny Atlas Quarterly</h3><p>相机包不应该仅仅是一件工具，它也可以是一款能够满足日常使用并且彰显个人风格的背包。<a href=\"http://www.tinyatlasquarterly.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Tiny Atlas Quarterly</a> 最近就和 Alite Designs 联手设计了一款休闲感十足的相机包 SOLAS，只要稍作调整它就能在背包、单肩包和托特包三种造型中切换。SOLAS 的内部空间经过精心的划分：不仅有为摄影装备设计的专用保护袋，还有能够容纳 13 寸电脑的隔层以及为太阳眼镜、手机等小物设计的取用方便的口袋。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/tinyatlas/tiny-atlas-solas-a-casual-camera-bag-for-photograp\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与众筹，早鸟价为 175 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608230032178dhIlOK39e1ZouRC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160823003218052PveiZOhxMY7KS.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.735294\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160823003216mncv83ib9eA0fpNQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.661765\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016082300321668lzZm4rUoQSYHpy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.822059\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608230032175kVQWeydDfbaiUjI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.897059\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160823003218YdxGrwZRpI9zU6kL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.827941\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Rock Chair by Da-sein Design Workshop</h3><p>只有当你从背面查看这套名为 Rock Chair 的椅子时，才会理解它名字的由来。这四张椅子由俄罗斯的工作坊 <a href=\"http://www.d1n-design.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Da-sein</a> 和设计师 Suzuki Kabuki 共同为东京 Tanoju 餐厅所打造，自成一体的椅面、扶手和椅背由俄罗斯榆木制成。为了打造出岩石一般的外框，设计师们对采自日本海岸上的石头进行了 3D 扫描，最后再通过电脑建模和 CNC 数控加工将那种粗旷的美丽呈现出来。设计师还保留了椅面部分的榆木木纹，正面温暖光滑，背面则显得冷酷崎岖。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160823003153Gkzv8WwI9Os1DLKP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160823003154PJegdU8q6pbakiTB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160823003154tkUOf2x8nZEpIBD3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.660952\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160823003153RnqEPVSWv6MITuCJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.658095\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160823003154nxi9Lz40rTaGYfXj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.658095\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160823003155Pr1TjetMpJQXkwVK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.658095\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Level by Permafrost &amp; Petter Knudsen</h3><p>在 2010 年举行的 Beyond Risør 大会上，来自 <a href=\"http://permafrost.no/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Permafrost</a> 工作室的工业设计师们和家具设计师 Petter Knudsen 展开了合作，试图打造一款在功能性和技术上有所突破的灯具。这款名为 <a href=\"http://permafrost.no/projects/level\" rel=\"nofollow\">Level</a> 的台灯就是他们最后在大会的 Beyond Light 展览中展出的作品，极简的造型使人眼前一亮：长长的白色铝制灯臂带给人一种轻盈的感觉，与略显厚重的圆柱形混凝土底座形成了鲜明的对比。安装在水平灯臂下方的 LED 灯采用了感应式设计，使用时只需要将手指沿着下侧滑动就能控制灯的开关，充满了互动性。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160823003121joO0qRCIT8AmxpaK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.736000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160823003122eOdmwuxsotPVaHQr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.732500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160823003123AIX95UjJai2YbED1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.736000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Love Cocoa by James Cadbury</h3><p>来自巧克力世家“吉百利”的 James Cadbury 在为母亲挑选生日礼物时发现了<a href=\"http://www.telegraph.co.uk/business/2016/06/30/cadbury-descendant-launches-chocolate-gift-delivery-brand-love-c/\" rel=\"nofollow\">一个尚未开发的市场</a>：他找不到能够直接将巧克力像信件一样隔天投送至邮箱的服务，不少品牌虽然提供送货，但也就意味着失去了打开邮箱后发现礼物的那份惊喜。为了填补这个空缺，他创立了手工巧克力品牌 <a href=\"https://www.lovecocoa.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Love Cocoa</a>，订制服务全部在线上完成，然后通过英国皇家邮政寄送。Love Cocoa 的巧克力包装并不花哨，仅通过不同颜色和重复的图案来表现六种风味，最后再和赠言卡片一起装进大小刚好能够塞进邮箱的“Hello, I’m yours”纸盒中。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160823002929csqH4BhdKnEVGLx2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.623611\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160823002949tWQL7KOaPSHTbGqR.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.623000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160823002932Bx1OLobCJFdA2y7c.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.623000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160823002933RlN8M6nYKtWjxhkC.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}